description: The GAN 356 M is a magnetic 3x3 speed cube featuring GAN's latest innovations. With smooth turning and excellent corner cutting, this cube is perfect for speedcubers of all levels.
An affordable magnetic 3x3 cube with excellent performance. Features dual adjustment system and comes pre-lubricated for smooth solving experience.
Professional magnetic 3x3 cube with strong magnets and customizable tensions. Excellent stability and speed for competitive solving.
Premium magnetic 3x3 featuring dual adjustment system and factory magnetization. Smooth performance with excellent corner cutting.
Competition-ready 3x3 cube with magnetic positioning system. Features excellent stability and fast turning for professional speedcubing.
GAN's flagship 3x3 cube with advanced magnetic system and UV coating. Professional choice for world-class speedcubers.
Dual adjustment magnetic 3x3 cube with enhanced turning and stability. Features premium design for competitive solving.
High-performance magnetic 4x4 cube with inner layer magnets. Smooth turning with excellent layer alignment for big cube solving.
Professional magnetic 5x5 cube with strong build quality. Features smooth layers and excellent stability for big cube enthusiasts.
Magnetic pyraminx with GAN's signature smooth turning. Perfect for those looking to expand beyond traditional 3x3 solving.
High-quality skewb puzzle with smooth corner cutting and excellent stability. Great for beginners and advanced solvers alike.
Professional dodecahedron puzzle with 12 faces. Magnetic positioning system ensures smooth and stable solving experience.
Shape-shifting puzzle based on 3x3 mechanism. Solve by shape rather than color for a unique twisty puzzle challenge.
Professional speedcubing timer with precision timing and competition-standard features. Essential accessory for serious speedcubers.
Professional solving mat with smooth surface and optimal size. Provides cushioning and prevents cube damage during practice sessions.
